{"tid":2052111,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"力天終於上市啦","createTime":"2020-06-05T09:23:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-05T09:23:45.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"45a0649f7dfca0ca0d00730459453336bd13625f","tid":2052111,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-05T09:23:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2662593/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E8%82%A1IPO%E3%80%91%E5%82%B3%E5%8A%9B%E5%A4%A9%E5%BD%B1%E6%A5%AD%E6%9C%80%E5%BF%AB%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E6%8B%9B%E8%82%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2662593%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2582%25A1IPO%25E3%2580%2591%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%258A%259B%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%2591%25A8%25E6%258B%259B%25E8%2582%25A1&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGUPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=d61b5f40\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2662593/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E8%82%A1IPO%E3%80%91%E5%82%B3%E5%8A%9B%E5%A4%A9%E5%BD%B1%E6%A5%AD%E6%9C%80%E5%BF%AB%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E6%8B%9B%E8%82%A1</a><br />\n<br />\n新股市場踏入旺季，除了華夏視聽準備於本季內上市，再有影視業務公司於本季內上市。市場消息指，內地電視劇發行公司力天影業於已通過上市聆訊，並計劃於最快於下周（6月9日）招股。<br />\n<br />\n公司的業務主要為：自製及買斷電視劇播映權許可、出售電視劇劇本、擔任電視系列劇播映權的發行代理、投資由集團擔任非執行製片人的電視劇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />阿添"}]}